Source: druid
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Andrew Otto <otto@wikimedia.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: http://druid.io

Package: druid-common
Architecture: all
Depends: openjdk-7-jre | java7-runtime, adduser, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Druid Common
 This package includes common Druid .jars including extensions and
 Hadoop Depdencies shipped with the Druid release.  It also includes the
 mysql-metadata-storage extension.

Package: druid-broker
Architecture: all
Depends: openjdk-7-jre | java7-runtime, adduser, ${misc:Depends}, druid-common
Description: Druid Broker Node
 This package installs init scripts for the Druid Broker node.

